Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If staying here becomes too tough for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,are you going to run away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always escaping, always finding my place...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think, I'll always end up here in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the story from before I confessed to Kon.